{"tid":2440623,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解一定要叫「巴打」唔可以叫老鐵？","createTime":"2021-03-10T05:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T11:14:55.000Z","uid":43557,"like":5,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7e2d3550471c2e37d298d61d22c5302a31fda73e","tid":2440623,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"乜撚野巴打呀？ <br />\n成日巴打前絲打後,me最撚憎 <br />\n何兄何弟呀？ <br />\n邊個係兄邊個係弟先？ <br />\n無lala自認契弟? <br />\n成班on79認親認戚 <br />\n<br />\n老鐵就唔同, <br />\n親切得黎又有d疏離感 <br />\n叫聲老鐵就好似尊敬人,自認自己是師弟, <br />\n唔同「巴打」好似懶熟懶fd咁 <br />\n<br />\n連登仔既論點來來去去都是「入鄉要隨俗」、「傳統」 <br />\n大陸人週街吐口水,返到大陸你會唔會入鄉隨俗,周街放飛機？ <br />\n有d野唔岩就要改,入唔鄉隨俗? <br />\n你阿婆以前要紮腳,你呢代洗唔洗紮腳呀？ <br />\n傳乜撚野統？ <br />\n連登仔唔好再咁盟塞啦！"},{"pid":"9fd048c8114fb370ebfcde03c913fc44be50ef54","tid":2440623,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229af4fc389380799ee96422869bab9c6073519f","tid":2440623,"uid":78243,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"老鐵雙擊666滿屏彈幕走一波 沒點訂閱點一下訂閱"},{"pid":"7fb5fb56576d008838713f4aba4f7d8e17e9a0a6","tid":2440623,"uid":268516,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:46:21.000Z","msg":"咁叫你Ching<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChing chong<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe295ac12359d587605edf573151134f2c881b8","tid":2440623,"uid":199804,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"俗語有云 打鐵趁熱<br />\n不打不相識 <br />\n老鐵=打左好多次=關係好好嘅老友"},{"pid":"62c1783149a2848c18355795d4a9c086fb118cce","tid":2440623,"uid":4187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"老鐵們走起😂😂👌"},{"pid":"872190989eef52742e5e938c78cfd4ae1e15e49b","tid":2440623,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot